            <h3>How To Ride</h3>
            <p>You can board dollar vans at designated stops, or hail them just like a taxi. 
                <strong>Queens, Flatbush</strong>: you can request a drop-off anywhere along the route. <strong>Chinatown, Flushing, Sunset Park</strong>: you must board and depart at designated stops.</p>
